title: The only premium thing about the Cristiano Ronaldo headphones is his name
text: The only premium thing about the Cristiano Ronaldo headphones is his name Saturday, 5 September 2015 (10 minutes ago) Cristiano Ronaldo or Lionel Messi, who's the best footballer in the world? To Monster, that question is unimportant, as the brand that once made Dr. Dre's Beats headphones has done custom cans for both of world football's top stars. Even so, today Monster would answer in favor of Mr. Ronaldo, having secured a partnership with the Real Madrid superstar to create his new line of Live Life Loud headphones.
